: 0.53em; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal;"><a href="https://www.wikiwand.com/zh-hans/%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83#citenote2" class="anch-link" style="box-sizing: border-box; background: 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(21, 89, 181); position: relative; transition: color 0.15s ease-out;">[2]</a></sup>。例如，投掷非均匀骰子得到的结果序列是独立同分布的，但掷出每个面朝上的概率并不相同。</p></section><section class="article_content" id="section_定义" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-bottom: 40px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16.5px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 2.32em; line-height: 1.4;"><span class="mw-headline" id="定义" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">定义</span><a href="https://zh-hans.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" target="_blank" onclick="event.stopPropagation()" class="edit_section tooltip_top tooltipstered" style="box-sizing: border-box; background: url(&quot;img/sprite.609db4c4.svg&quot;) -194px -162px no-repeat; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(21, 89, 181); position: relative; transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 26px; height: 26px; opacity: 0; transform: translateX(10px);"></a></h2><p style="box-sizing: